- brown beef trimmings in pan
- chop shallots and add to pan to caramelise too
- once shallots start caramelising, add chopped thyme, bay leaf, and garlic and add to pan to toast
- leave pan on high and add red wine
- add stock (/espagnol sauce) and reduce
- strain
- add red wine vinegar and butter at lowish temp to emulsify
